  "detailed_description": "In this retro platformer, the goal is simple. <strong>Get to the exit door.</strong> Of course, it's never just that simple…<br><br>You begin the game trapped in prison.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768080/extras/f4b46c5f572c1ab1b18b1bbc86cead6b.avif?t=1712307912\" width=616 height=252 /></span><br><br>First you must break out, which is a task in itself – but breaking out of prison is never easy, unless you're Stallone! But it's simple once you know how…<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768080/extras/c2001bd41edc5f11d6255d1a7da37117.avif?t=1712307912\" width=616 height=252 /></span><br><br>After that, you'll make your way into a complex network of levels which you must traverse.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768080/extras/4d93f6a5f0fe6a0bc665ddb89c748e1a.avif?t=1712307912\" width=616 height=252 /></span><br><br>The path from door to door becomes increasingly difficult.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768080/extras/cada6f6486e17f98d9e53120678fa8af.avif?t=1712307912\" width=616 height=252 /></span><br><br>Ingenious traps – each one designed to kill you – litter your pathway. Some you can simply jump over. Others you can crouch underneath. However, there are those where you'll need luck, skill and speed.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768080/extras/4fb6c78208a3f217f51683c380e31aae.avif?t=1712307912\" width=616 height=252 /></span><br><br>And two questions remain. Are you really free? Indeed, who's the one who's really trapped…?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768080/extras/2a5215c931f9266f96ece3a633f03588.avif?t=1712307912\" width=616 height=252 /></span><br><br>Maybe you'll choose to stay a prisoner and escape faster and faster each time. Perhaps even death might be out of the quesiton…",
  "about_the_game": "In this retro platformer, the goal is simple. <strong>Get to the exit door.</strong> Of course, it's never just that simple…<br><br>You begin the game trapped in prison.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768080/extras/f4b46c5f572c1ab1b18b1bbc86cead6b.avif?t=1712307912\" width=616 height=252 /></span><br><br>First you must break out, which is a task in itself – but breaking out of prison is never easy, unless you're Stallone! But it's simple once you know how…<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768080/extras/c2001bd41edc5f11d6255d1a7da37117.avif?t=1712307912\" width=616 height=252 /></span><br><br>After that, you'll make your way into a complex network of levels which you must traverse.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768080/extras/4d93f6a5f0fe6a0bc665ddb89c748e1a.avif?t=1712307912\" width=616 height=252 /></span><br><br>The path from door to door becomes increasingly difficult.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768080/extras/cada6f6486e17f98d9e53120678fa8af.avif?t=1712307912\" width=616 height=252 /></span><br><br>Ingenious traps – each one designed to kill you – litter your pathway. Some you can simply jump over. Others you can crouch underneath. However, there are those where you'll need luck, skill and speed.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2768080/extras/4fb6c78208a3f217f51683c380e31aae.avif?t=1712307912\" width=616 height=252 /></span><br><br>And two questions remain. Are you really free? Indeed, who's the one who's really trapped…?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><